             was indicted for <rs id="t18300708-204-off1150" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300708-204-off1150" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300708-204-off1150" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18300708-204-cd1151" type="crimeDate">5th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300708-204-off1150 t18300708-204-cd1151"></join>, 1 copper, value 20s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18300708-204-victim1307" type="victimName">
                        John 
                        Gibbons
                     <interp inst="t18300708-204-victim1307" type="surname" value="Gibbons"></interp>
